<b>Styling:</b>
<ul>
<li>Adapt styling to dark and light theme.</li>
<li>Prevent pie chart labels from overlapping.</li>
<li>Improve layout of tables and navigation.</li>
</ul>

<b>Crashes:</b>
<ul>
<li>In case the given ntopng user name has insufficients rights to see the data, a warning is now shown.</li>
<li>In case the user mapping is derived from the custom attribute "ntopng username" and this attribute is empty, all ntop links will now be hidden.</li>
</ul>
